cast.overview: After their late former Captain is framed, Lowrey and Burnett try to clear his name, only to end up on the run themselves.
cast.title: Bad Boys: Ride or Die

details.biography: Jay Shetty is an English author, former Hindu monk, and life coach of British Indian descent. As the host of the podcast On Purpose, his guests have included Alicia Keys, Khloe Kardashian, and Kobe Bryant, resulting in over 300 million downloads. Jay Shetty is known for Wisdom Goes Viral (2020), Jay Shetty (2020), Kings Of The Internet (2022) and The Perfect Love Story (2021). He has been married to Radhi Devlukia-Shetty since April 2016.
details.name: Jay Shetty
